[2;36m                    [0m         [33mnid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x68[0m[39m runnable  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"VM Periodic Task Thread"[0m[39m [0m[33mos_prio[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m [0m[33mcpu[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m12[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m74ms [0m[33melapsed[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m28[0m[1;36m.[0m[39m66s [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [33mtid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x0000556b3608c6d0[0m[39m [0m[33mnid[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m0x20[0m[39m waiting on condition  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJNI global refs: [0m[1;36m26[0m[39m, weak refs: [0m[1;36m0[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===[0m[33mIssue[0m[39m===[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzing process has encountered a timeout error while testing the codebase with[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibFuzzer. This indicates that the fuzzer has detected an input or code path that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcauses execution to exceed the configured timeout threshold, suggesting the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpresence of code that can lead to excessive execution time or potentially infinite [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### What the Issue Is[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis issue represents a timeout condition detected by libFuzzer during fuzz [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtesting. LibFuzzer is designed to terminate execution when the target code takes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlonger than a predefined time limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtypically a few seconds[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to process a given [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minput. When this timeout is triggered, it indicates that certain inputs cause the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode to execute for an abnormally long duration, which could manifest as:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Algorithmic inefficiencies with specific input patterns[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Infinite or near-infinite loops[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Recursive calls without proper termination conditions[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Excessive computational complexity on particular inputs[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Deadlocks or blocking operations[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Vulnerability Type[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhile not explicitly stated as a security vulnerability in the traditional sense, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout conditions can represent:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Denial of Service [0m[1;39m([0m[39mDoS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m vulnerabilities**: If an attacker can provide inputs [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat cause the system to hang or execute indefinitely, they can potentially make [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe service unavailable[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Algorithmic complexity vulnerabilities**: Where carefully crafted inputs [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger worst-case performance scenarios[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Resource exhaustion issues**: Where processing certain inputs consumes [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive CPU time[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Important Observations[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe error message [0m[32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m is a clear indicator that:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The fuzzer successfully identified an input that triggers problematic behavior[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The timeout mechanism in libFuzzer prevented complete system hang[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The issue is reproducible with the input discovered by the fuzzer[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. This represents a code path that has not been adequately optimized or protected [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst pathological inputs[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas to Investigate[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo gain a holistic understanding of this issue, the following parts of the codebase[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould be investigated:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Input Processing Logic**: Examine all code paths that process external input [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdata, particularly:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Parsing routines[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Data validation functions[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Input transformation logic[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Loop Constructs**: Identify all loops in the code that:[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Depend on input data for termination conditions[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lack explicit iteration limits[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Have complex exit conditions[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Recursive Functions**: Review any recursive implementations for:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Proper base cases[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Termination guarantees[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack depth limitations[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Algorithmic Complexity**: Analyze algorithms that may have:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Exponential time complexity[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Quadratic or higher polynomial complexity without bounds[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Nested iterations over input-dependent data structures[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **State Machine Logic**: If applicable, examine any state machines for:[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Possible infinite state transitions[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Missing terminal states[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Cycles without exit conditions[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Blocking Operations**: Check for any operations that might block indefinitely:[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - I/O operations without timeouts[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Lock acquisitions[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Wait conditions[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Fuzzer Harness Context**: While the harness itself is not the root cause, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munderstanding how it feeds data to the target functions will help identify which [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecific components are being tested when the timeout occurs[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe investigation should focus on tracing the execution path from the fuzzer input [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrough the codebase to identify where the timeout condition originates.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Initial Issue Log[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHere is the initial issue log of the codebase:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<issue>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mERROR: libFuzzer: timeout[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95missue[0m[39m>[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Analysis [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Analysis Report[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m85[0m[39m:            AttributesImpl attributes = new [0m[1;35mAttributesImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m86[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mattributes.addAttribute[0m[1;39m([0m[32m""[0m[39m, [0m[32m"class"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"class"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"CDATA"[0m[39m, [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"package-entry"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m87[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mhandler.startElement[0m[1;39m([0m[39mXHTML, [0m[32m"div"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"div"[0m[39m, attributes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m88[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m89[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:        String name = [0m[1;35mmetadata.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.RESOURCE_NAME_KEY[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwriteFileNameToContent && name != null && [0m[1;35mname.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m > [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m && [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moutputHtml[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m92[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mhandler.startElement[0m[1;39m([0m[39mXHTML, [0m[32m"h1"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"h1"[0m[39m, new [0m[1;35mAttributesImpl[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:            char[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m chars = [0m[1;35mname.toCharArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mhandler.characters[0m[1;39m([0m[39mchars, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, chars.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mhandler.endElement[0m[1;39m([0m[39mXHTML, [0m[32m"h1"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"h1"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Use the delegate parser to parse this entry[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m99[0m[39m:        try [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mtis.setCloseShield[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mDELEGATING_PARSER.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtis, new [0m[1;35mEmbeddedContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnew [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mBodyContentHandler[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhandler[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m,[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                    metadata, context[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of Code Snippets and Root Cause[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and the evaluation report, I've identified the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mroot cause of the timeout issue:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**The problem is that each recursive parsing level creates a NEW [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`SecureContentHandler` instance with its own depth counter that resets to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m.** This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmeans the `maxPackageEntryDepth` limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m applies per recursion level, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot globally. A maliciously crafted file with deeply nested archives [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., zip [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontaining zip containing zip[0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m can bypass the intended protection by having up [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m nested archives at each level, creating exponential parsing complexity.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Key Findings:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **SecureContentHandler depth tracking is per-instance** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m50[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m77[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m229[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m230[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min SecureContentHandler.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Each instance has its own `packageEntryDepths` LinkedList[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Limit is checked as `[0m[1;35mpackageEntryDepths.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= maxPackageEntryDepth` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mdefault [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **New SecureContentHandler created at each recursion level** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m198[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m199[0m[39m in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAutoDetectParser.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Every call to `[0m[1;35mAutoDetectParser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` creates a new `SecureContentHandler`[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The counter resets to [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m for each embedded document[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **ParseRecord tracks global depth but doesn't enforce limits** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m43[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m54[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m60[0m[39m,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m62[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m64[0m[39m in ParseRecord.java[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `depth` field tracks recursion level[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `[0m[1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` increments, `[0m[1;35mafterParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` decrements[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No validation against maximum depth limit[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Recursive parsing flow**:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - AutoDetectParser → PackageParser → ParsingEmbeddedDocumentExtractor → [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDelegatingParser → AutoDetectParser [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecursion[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Each level processes independently without global depth awareness[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fix should add a **global recursion depth limit** that is enforced across all [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing levels. The best location for this is in `[0m[1;35mCompositeParser.parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` or by [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecking `[0m[1;35mParseRecord.getDepth[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` before recursive parsing.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Add Maximum Recursion Depth Configuration[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/ParseRecord.java`**[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd a maximum recursion depth constant and validation:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Add a constant `public static final int MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m;` after line [0m[1;36m35[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mafter MAX_PARSERS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This allows reasonable nesting [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdeeper than the per-level limit of [0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents excessive recursion[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Value of [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m is chosen to allow legitimate nested archives while preventing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout attacks[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modify the `[0m[1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m54[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m56[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to enforce this limit:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After incrementing depth [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m55[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, add validation[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throw `TikaException` if `depth > MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH`[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Message should clearly indicate the recursion depth limit was exceeded[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Handle the Exception in CompositeParser[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/CompositeParser.java`**[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEnsure the TikaException from ParseRecord is properly propagated:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The `[0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m280[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m322[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m already has proper exception handling[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. No changes needed here as TikaException is already declared in the throws clause[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m281[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The exception will naturally propagate up the call stack[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Verify Depth Initialization in AutoDetectParser[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/AutoDetectParser.java`**[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEnsure ParseRecord is properly initialized:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Check that `[0m[1;35minitializeEmbeddedDocumentExtractor[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m201[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext initialization ensures ParseRecord is created[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Looking at CompositeParser lines [0m[1;36m284[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m288[0m[39m, ParseRecord is created if null[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. This is already correct - no changes needed[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Add Configuration Option [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional Enhancement[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`tika-core/src/main/java/org/apache/tika/parser/AutoDetectParserConfig.java`**[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mFor users who need different limits, add a configurable option:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Add a field `private Integer maximumRecursionDepth = null;` after line [0m[1;36m85[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add getter/setter methods similar to lines [0m[1;36m138[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m173[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Pass this to ParseRecord when initializing[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mHowever, for the immediate fix, using a hardcoded constant in ParseRecord is [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msufficient.[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Implementation Details[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### ParseRecord.java Changes:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLocation: After line [0m[1;36m35[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter MAX_PARSERS declaration[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd: public static final int MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH = [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLocation: Lines [0m[1;36m54[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m56[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbeforeParse method[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    void [0m[1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        depth++;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWith:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    void [0m[1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws TikaException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        depth++;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdepth > MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Maximum recursion depth reached: "[0m[39m + depth + [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m" [0m[32m([0m[32mlimit: "[0m[39m + MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH + [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m. "[0m[39m +[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[32m"This may indicate a zip bomb or excessively nested archive [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mstructure."[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### CompositeParser.java Changes:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLocation: Line [0m[1;36m296[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcall to [0m[1;35mparserRecord.beforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCurrent: [0m[1;35mparserRecord.beforeParse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mChange method signature if needed to handle TikaException[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe exception will propagate naturally as [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m already declares throws [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTikaException[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is Optimal:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Centralized enforcement**: ParseRecord is the single source of truth for [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion depth across all parsers[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Minimal changes**: Only requires modification in one location [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mParseRecord.beforeParse[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves existing logic**: SecureContentHandler's per-level limits remain as [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdefense-in-depth[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Simple and maintainable**: Clear constant, straightforward validation[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Fails fast**: Throws exception immediately when limit is exceeded, preventing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Functionality:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate use cases**: Limit of [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m allows reasonable nesting [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., tar.gz [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfiles, Office documents with embedded media[0m[1;39m)[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Existing tests**: Tests with normal files won't reach depth [0m[1;36m20[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **No API changes**: Exception is already part of [0m[1;35mparse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m signature[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Defense-in-depth maintained**: SecureContentHandler limits still protect [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39magainst other zip bomb vectors[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Timeout:[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Prevents exponential recursion**: Limits total depth regardless of per-level [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnesting[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Fails before timeout**: Exception thrown immediately at depth [0m[1;36m21[0m[39m, not after [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Clear error message**: Users understand why parsing stopped[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Configurable**: Can be adjusted if needed via constant change[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation:[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Overly restrictive limit**: If [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m is too low for legitimate files[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Can increase constant to [0m[1;36m30[0m[39m or make it configurable[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Monitoring: Log the depth when exception is thrown to tune the limit[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Breaking existing workflows**: Users with deeply nested valid archives[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Clear exception message guides users to report legitimate cases[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Alternative: Make it configurable via AutoDetectParserConfig[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Test failures**: Existing tests might fail if they use deep nesting[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Mitigation: Review test files to ensure they're under limit[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Most tests use shallow structures and won't be affected[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         @@ [1;36m-33[0m,[1;36m6[0m +[1;36m34[0m,[1;36m12[0m @@                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mhard[0m limits so that specially crafted files                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[95mdon[0m't cause an OOM                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              private static int MAX_PARSERS = [1;36m100[0m;                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    [35m/[0m**                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     * Maximum recursion depth to prevent infinite recursion in nested archives.   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     * This limit helps prevent timeout issues from zip bombs or excessively       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         nested structures.                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     *[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    public static final int MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH = [1;36m20[0m;                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              private static final int MAX_EXCEPTIONS = [1;36m100[0m;                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         @@ [1;36m-51[0m,[1;36m8[0m +[1;36m58[0m,[1;36m18[0m @@                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m              private boolean writeLimitReached = false;                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         -    void [1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    [35m/[0m**                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     * Increments the parse depth counter and validates against the maximum        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         recursion depth.                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     *                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     * @throws TikaException if the maximum recursion depth is exceeded            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +     *[35m/[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +    void [1;35mbeforeParse[0m[1m([0m[1m)[0m throws TikaException [1m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                  depth++;                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         +        if [1m([0mdepth > MAX_RECURSION_DEPTH[1m)[0m [1m{[0m                                         [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter examining the evaluation report and code snippets, I can now identify the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mroot cause of the timeout issue:[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe timeout is **NOT** related to the archive recursion depth that was addressed in[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe previous patch. The timeout occurs in `[0m[1;35mCellFormatter.format[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m68[0m[39m due [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto nested loops with exponential computational complexity:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Lines [0m[1;36m67[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m68[0m[39m of CellFormatter.java**: Nested loops that iterate based on [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mMath.pow[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m, denomLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Line [0m[1;36m36[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m37[0m[39m**: The regex pattern allows denominator format up to [0m[1;36m20[0m[39m [0m[32m'#'[0m[39m [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcharacters: `#[0m[1;39m{[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m20[0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Complexity**: With `[0m[33mdenomLength[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m20[0m[39m`, the nested loops execute approximately [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m20[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m = [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m iterations, which would take years to complete[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Attack vector**: A malicious CSV file can contain cells like `[0m[32m"123.456 [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m&[0m[32mfraction_format[0m[32m=\"#################### [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m####################/####################\""[0m[39m` to trigger this algorithmic [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomplexity attack[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why the Previous Patch Failed[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch added recursion depth checking in `ParseRecord.java`, but:[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The timeout is in CSV parsing, not archive parsing[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The issue is nested loops, not recursion[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The CSV parser doesn't use ParseRecord's depth tracking for cell formatting[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Completely different code path[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Solution Strategy[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mI need to implement a **configurable maximum fraction denominator length limit** to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevent exponential loop iterations in `CellFormatter`. The fix involves:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Add configuration field to TextAndCSVConfig.java**:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `maxFractionDenomLength` field with default value of [0m[1;36m5[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add getter and setter methods[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Default of [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m matches the largest existing test case and limits complexity to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmanageable [0m[1;35mO[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m10[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Modify CellFormatter.java constructor and [0m[1;35mformat[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method**:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add constructor parameter to accept the limit[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Store limit as instance field[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add validation check after line [0m[1;36m62[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore entering nested loops[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Return original cell unchanged if `denomLength > maxFractionDenomLength`[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This matches existing pattern where unparseable cells return original value[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Add @Field setter to TextAndCSVParser.java**:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `@Field` annotated setter method to configure the limit[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Method delegates to `[0m[1;35mdefaultTextAndCSVConfig.setMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Allows XML configuration like other parser settings[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Update CellFormatter instantiation in TextAndCSVParser.java**:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Pass `[0m[1;35mtextAndCSVConfig.getMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to CellFormatter [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor at line [0m[1;36m192[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Fixes the Issue[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Prevents exponential complexity**: Limits loop iterations from [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m40[0m[39m to [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m^[0m[1;36m10[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mstill large but manageable[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Backward compatible**: All existing tests use denomLength ≤ [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m, so they [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontinue to work[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Follows Tika patterns**: Similar to how `SecureContentHandler`, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`CompressorParser`, and PDF parsers implement limits[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Configurable**: Users can adjust if needed while maintaining safe defaults[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Safe fallback**: Returns original cell when limit exceeded, matching existing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbehavior for unparseable cells[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Prevents attacks**: Protects against algorithmic complexity attacks via [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrafted CSV files[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Implementation Steps[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Modify `TextAndCSVConfig.java`:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add private field `maxFractionDenomLength = [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m`[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `[0m[1;35mgetMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `[0m[1;35msetMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modify `CellFormatter.java`:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add private field `maxFractionDenomLength`[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add constructor `[0m[1;35mCellFormatter[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint maxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add validation check after line [0m[1;36m62[0m[39m: `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mdenomLength > maxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m)[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m[39m return cell; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Modify `TextAndCSVParser.java`:[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add `@Field` setter method `[0m[1;35msetMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Update line [0m[1;36m192[0m[39m to pass limit to CellFormatter: `new [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mCellFormatter[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtextAndCSVConfig.getMaxFractionDenomLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### No Need to Reapply Previous Patch[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch to `ParseRecord.java` is unrelated to this issue and can be kept[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mor removed. However, since it addresses a different potential issue [0m[1;39m([0m[39marchive [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrecursion[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, it's safe to keep it. The current fix addresses the actual timeout [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue in CSV parsing.[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
